snippet.title: SimRail - The Railway Simulator: Cargo Pack DLC | Relase trailer
snippet.description:
SimRail - The Railway Simulator: Cargo Pack DLC now available on Steam!
🚂 https://store.steampowered.com/app/2868050/SimRail__The_Railway_Simulator_Cargo_Pack/
 
The King of Polish freight mainlines, strong as a bull - take the helm of the legendary ET22 locomotive and lead heavy freight trains with new wagons!
